# Against the Infernal

With every dark pact and sacrificial victim, Hell's power grows. As streets become playgrounds for demons and infernalist cults proliferate like wildfire, many proclaim that the world teeters on the brink of annihilation. 

The Cabal is not deaf to the screams of fear and agony. The Lucignostic College, led by experienced infernauts like Refia Graennah and Corbulus Senex, has formed specifically to fight this threat. But the calls for action are coming from all sects, cults and factions.

