The demonic threat can no longer be ignored. At the foretold hour, we have performed an ancient ritual to sacrifice the voices of one-tenth of Cabal members - present, past and future - and bring forth the Crimson Choir. The price for invoking this eldritch entity is unspeakably high in more than one sense, but the salvation of the world is paramount.
